OL,3,CCouncils warn Chancellor that support
OL,4,Cfor most vulnerable is under threat
OL,6,FGroups representing all 350 local
OL,7,Fauthorities across England and Wales
OL,8,Fhave warned the Chancellor that any
OL,9,Ffunding reductions for councils would
OL,10,Fbe "disastrous".
OL,12,FA letter sent to Rachel Reeves ahead
OL,13,Fof the Budget - and seen by ITV News -
OL,14,Fcalls for "immediate action to
OL,15,Fstabilise council finances and protect
OL,16,Fvital services" - with a stark warning
OL,17,Fof the alternative.
