OL,3,CCouncils warn Chancellor that support
OL,4,Cfor most vulnerable is under threat
OL,6,F"It is clear to us that without this
OL,7,Faction the ability of councils to
OL,8,Fdeliver crucial services, including
OL,9,Fsupporting some of the most vulnerable
OL,10,Fin society... is under threat."
OL,12,FThe letter, signed by a number of
OL,13,Forganisations, including the Local
OL,14,FGovernment Association and the County
OL,15,FCouncils Network, claims councils have
OL,16,Ffaced a "perfect financial storm".
