OL,3,CCouncils warn Chancellor that support
OL,4,Cfor most vulnerable is under threat
OL,6,F"We do not underestimate the difficult
OL,7,Fdecisions you will have to take in
OL,8,Fyour first Budget," it said. "But
OL,9,Fstabilising the local government
OL,10,Fsector financially will not only
OL,11,Fprotect key services, it will also
OL,12,Fprovide a return on investment to the
OL,13,Ftax-payer, while improving outcomes
OL,14,Ffor the people and places councils
OL,15,Fserve."
