OL,4,Cfor most vulnerable is under threat
OL,6,FThe letter highlights particular areas
OL,7,Fwhere financial pressures have
OL,8,Fintensified, including the placement
OL,9,Fcosts in children's social care (which
OL,10,Fhas risen in real-terms by 25.7 per
OL,11,Fcent since 2019/20), rising demand in
OL,12,Fadult social care and a rise in
OL,13,Fhomelessness.
